// GENERATED-ish: snapshots of the production public catalogs, embedded as Dart
// string literals so the demo Fake repository resolves them synchronously (no
// asset/rootBundle I/O). rootBundle.loadString resolves on the real wall clock,
// which never advances under flutter_test's fake clock — a screen showing a
// CircularProgressIndicator while awaiting it spins forever and pumpAndSettle
// times out. Embedding sidesteps that entirely and keeps the running web/Android
// demo showing the full ~90-source catalog and the real voice samples.
//
// Source of record: assets/demo/sources_catalog.json + voices_catalog.json
// (snapshotted from GET /v1/sources/catalog and /v1/voices/catalog). The live
// ApiAppRepository fetches those same public endpoints once auth lands.

